				<div class="comment-body"><p>The reason the link did not work when you tried it is because Loncon 3 had not quite yet posted the detailed results. The link is correct and began working about fifteen minutes after the ceremony. We elected to go ahead and publish the announcement and the link so they would be out there as soon as possible even though the link to the details took a few more minutes to actually resolve.</p>
