				<div class="comment-body"><p>Well, this was largely disappointing results. I thought the voters would come to their senses and declare &#8220;Frozen&#8221; a definitive winner of the &#8220;Best Dramatic Presentation (Long Form)&#8221; award, but instead, &#8220;Gravity&#8221; (which I obviously would not have placed my vote on; I actually thought &#8220;Catching Fire&#8221; would be a more fitting contender) somehow stole the award. The one time I actually care about this type of award and you mess it up like this. That&#8217;s it, the Hugo Awards are dead to me. Really disappointed&#8230;</p>
</div>

